{"type": "article", "id": 16343, "title": "把热狗拍成公路主题，7-11是想说什么？", "description": "“带我走吧。”", "date": "2015-10-20T18:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2863, "name": "便利店"}, {"id": 14457, "name": "7-Eleven"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605220134Lsdj4hW9bmS1eBai.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t炽热的加热灯下，皱皮的热狗在不知停歇地滚动。还有多种口味的思乐冰机器，轻触按钮，扑满的 <span>16 </span>寸大杯思乐冰能让你捧着嚼上好一会儿。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>7-Eleven </span>便利店把这些标志性的食物做成了一组公路主题的宣传海报。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201312JBjEcnr894xv0gD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220131KV4dawZQJuUnykpY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220131fTA0GcJ483IxtpdH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t思乐冰成了信号灯，吸管化身温度计，热狗好像是烈日下滚烫的高速公路……这组创意来自温哥华广告公司 <span>Spring</span>，意在表现 <span>7-Eleven </span>便利店的食物统统可以带着走 <span>(ON THE GO)</span>，是公路司机们的好伙伴，近 <span>50 </span>年来 <span>7-Eleven </span>也是美国高速公路休息站上最常见的一块牌子。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>2013 年 </span><span>7-Eleven </span><span>曾将美国超过五</span><span>万间连锁店翻新，希望通过更换 </span><span>LOGO </span><span>和店面设计摆脱此前油腻的、供应香烟、糖类和脂肪的不良形象，以更好地迎合千禧一代和女性群体。<span>在此之前，</span><span>7-Eleven </span><span>的目标人群主要是随地吐痰的货车司机、师奶式的家庭主妇，以及骑着小轮车的熊孩子。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220132nCafwK3bDZvQR28G.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>7-Eleven“变身前”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220133KGr5MHYtZPLjcE7i.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t7-Eleven“变身后”\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220133eQaR0bwj1AYB5EkI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.615625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}